stac_uav_bc

The goal of stac_uav_bc is to document and serve out our UAV collection for British Columbia. It is organized by watershed and can be queried by location and time using our API via the lovely rstac R package and QGIS (v3.42+). Still a work in progress but currently functioning.


Drone imagery download and viewer links. NOTE: Links to viewer current may need to be manually altered in browser to begin with http vs https! This should be resolved soon.

As of QGIS 3.42 - ONE can also access stac items (orthoimagery, Digital Surface Models and Digital Terrain Models in our case) directly via the Data Source Manager. See a blog with details here. It looks like this in the th Layer / Data Source Manager toolbar in QGIS:
